{"tid":2273043,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[家居維修] 馬桶水長流","createTime":"2020-11-05T12:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T13:18:45.000Z","uid":30104,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d49428b8190402d5895ad30f9f956cd2ebbac0c1","tid":2273043,"uid":30104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"最近大廈停完咸水之後 馬桶就不停流水 (水箱滿水仍不斷入水)<br />\n以前試過折開下圖1.號位, 清下舊膠 D 沙泥就冇事<br />\n例如咁 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QaeA4dV-Q6M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQaeA4dV-Q6M&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8hAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=28561052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QaeA4dV-Q6M</a><br />\n<br />\n今次照做<br />\n但呢次1號位入邊冇問題<br />\nD 水不停起 2.號位 D窿流出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算我用手指塞住1號位 入水個窿都係咁<br />\n有冇得搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZ830Bh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZ830Bh.jpg&h=aee3302d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e966861d90c0fa53ddf3e0d529d6e4f769e5596d","tid":2273043,"uid":1565,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"排水閥出左事"},{"pid":"faa0b2eb1e1a381837107b12e437aaf428440c1b","tid":2273043,"uid":30104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e966861d90c0fa53ddf3e0d529d6e4f769e5596d","tid":2273043,"uid":1565,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"排水閥出左事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"排水閥冇問題儲到水<br />\n係不停入水, 超過正常水位漏返出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9c1b3a6b990750f94dc363ac9824f6879c91dd","tid":2273043,"uid":1565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faa0b2eb1e1a381837107b12e437aaf428440c1b","tid":2273043,"uid":30104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e966861d90c0fa53ddf3e0d529d6e4f769e5596d","tid":2273043,"uid":1565,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"排水閥出左事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"排水閥冇問題儲到水<br />\n係不停入水, 超過正常水位漏返出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"邊度漏水？ 水箱蓋邊度漏？"},{"pid":"96357b2549c69c96bec59d3d0e350be55ef1a5c3","tid":2273043,"uid":182543,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:05:31.000Z","msg":"成抽換唔好研究，我試過半夜入水位唔停漏到全屋濕晒"},{"pid":"a8a2ebe1a20545034aada0f04c8c45d6bbe94d2b","tid":2273043,"uid":59691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1JLJ08j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1JLJ08j.jpg&h=590a010c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n1, 注水浮波升起<br />\n2, 升起左後推高條膠關入水位<br />\n入面有野斷左關唔到入水位<br />\n去五金舖買翻個佰幾蚊自己換"},{"pid":"2d3ac717d786a8c378c13e83b7258e167457fd04","tid":2273043,"uid":68098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"1)個蓋可以打開<br />\n<br />\n你應該膠圈底出水位爆左<br />\n<br />\n去五金舖<br />\n買<br />\nfluid master<br />\naround $75<br />\n<br />\n左右<br />\n你成串換啦"},{"pid":"457dbbdd00b0c2ff0c12b95d614201ffc35c3e9b","tid":2273043,"uid":68098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2d3ac717d786a8c378c13e83b7258e167457fd04","tid":2273043,"uid":68098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"1)個蓋可以打開<br />\n<br />\n你應該膠圈底出水位爆左<br />\n<br />\n去五金舖<br />\n買<br />\nfluid master<br />\naround $75<br />\n<br />\n左右<br />\n你成串換啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rw0ucno.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRw0ucno.jpg&h=68ba5ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢紅色位係個蓋入面<br />\n有一個膠圈<br />\n係拎黎壓住底既出水位<br />\n<br />\n個出水位因為老化<br />\n可能有地方斷左<br />\n你個膠圈壓唔實<br />\n所以長出水"},{"pid":"a3c7abad66e62f784460312da636f19623e9a02c","tid":2273043,"uid":30104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"OK 唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日去五金買成抽換"},{"pid":"00d46591fc4dde9b9e956c34a94fd58252c4ac7c","tid":2273043,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"成舊換"},{"pid":"8d76c0f20b0ba2188892319bb5a45742feb57352","tid":2273043,"uid":188859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"請問點樣可以減少入水時候嘅嘈音？<br />\n<br />\n我入水個掣冇開盡，因為試過開盡會滿瀉水，關細左個入水掣又會有水嘅摩擦聲造成嘈音"},{"pid":"3e0112a6047f87d7b21ad422c5e1f4385322a3de","tid":2273043,"uid":188859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:26:02.000Z","msg":"另外你條片真心好好，簡單易明"},{"pid":"7b7b0a4bdca90312a33f8b42110dc174b97096e0","tid":2273043,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d76c0f20b0ba2188892319bb5a45742feb57352","tid":2273043,"uid":188859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"請問點樣可以減少入水時候嘅嘈音？<br />\n<br />\n我入水個掣冇開盡，因為試過開盡會滿瀉水，關細左個入水掣又會有水嘅摩擦聲造成嘈音"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"1)是否同類型水制<br />\n<br />\n2)是否high pitch 嘈聲"},{"pid":"04046ca98469e094b27b441fbc397acd6573b90b","tid":2273043,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d76c0f20b0ba2188892319bb5a45742feb57352","tid":2273043,"uid":188859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"請問點樣可以減少入水時候嘅嘈音？<br />\n<br />\n我入水個掣冇開盡，因為試過開盡會滿瀉水，關細左個入水掣又會有水嘅摩擦聲造成嘈音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T18:30:27.000Z","msg":"點解開盡會滿瀉先，成個入水閥換左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1df0b35fc322873bb69dabbfe1201936de5651","tid":2273043,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score